snippet.title: Monaco 2 | Release Date Announcement Trailer | Humble Games
snippet.description:
Time to start coming up with your alibi because Monaco 2 sneaks onto PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X|S on April 10, 2025! Choose from eight characters with unique heist-changing abilities as you and up to three friends attempt to steal anything that isn’t bolted to the floor.

Wishlist today! 
Steam: https://bit.ly/Monaco2_on_Steam
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9p692dqm7n3j
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10011023/
